publisher			Animate Objects							
publish_time	 2016年4月8日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							VReakout is a modern re-imagining of the classic brick breaker genre with a virtual reality twist and designed for the HTC Vive VR System. Your mission is in deep space where you clear the areas before getting sucked into the Black Hole. Don't look back.Break through the levels within the time limit. How many balls will it take you?Work around the ice cube barriers! Perfect your timing to defeat the pulsating cubes.Bonus points for speed! The challenge continues with a steady release of updates containing power-ups, crazy awesome levels and environments, physics manipulation combined with an action packed frenetic pace and music that's on point.						
